Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:17.40,GEM,,0,0,0,,What's up with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.32,GEM,,0,0,0,,Did the whole town get up on the wrong side of the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.92,GEM,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're guarding the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:25.12,GEM,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind, this is an important relic to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:29.08,GEM,,0,0,0,,They might think we're grave robbers or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.40,GEM,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen, we're good, clean-cut boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.40,GEM,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:37.76,GEM,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll just let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:44.92,GEM,,0,0,0,,I said, we're not here to loot your crappy old graves, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:45.92,GEM,,0,0,0,,That didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:46.92,GEM,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.92,GEM,,0,0,0,,Something's not quite right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:56.64,GEM,,0,0,0,,You don't think there could be that many of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:57.64,GEM,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.72,GEM,,0,0,0,,Their form is starting to ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:01.72,GEM,,0,0,0,,Golems!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:14.32,GEM,,0,0,0,,Why do they have to show up wherever we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:15.32,GEM,,0,0,0,,We'd better retreat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.32,GEM,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what are a bunch of golems doing in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:17.32,GEM,,0,0,0,,You're asking the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:32.12,GEM,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell your friends they've got to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:45.84,GEM,,0,0,0,,The streets are about to be flooded with real nasty creatures and with beady eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:49.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,Is this the place where the science said always a golden town?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,This place has been in ruins for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,I knew something wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,But now we've got the whole thing figured out, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:53.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,Tell them these things won't pass next time, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.36,GEM,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
